          <updateDate>2018-06-06T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Keep Buying American Act of 2018</b> </p> <p>This bill directs each agency required to submit reports under Executive Order 13788, titled &quot;Buy American and Hire American,&quot; to make each report available to the public and Congress at the same time it submits the report to the Department of Commerce and the Office of Management and Budget.</p> <p>Each agency that was previously required to submit a report under such order shall make each report available to the public and to Congress.</p>]]></text>
